{"tid":2323971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[多圖] 正妹媽媽鼻子長黑頭粉刺 擠一下竟變怪病腫成「象鼻」！","createTime":"2020-12-13T14:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T09:39:30.000Z","uid":82917,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aaa962b64609125533bf244024b7263516873abe","tid":2323971,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xhh9PTN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXhh9PTN.png&h=bf4549dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201210/XNK3OYPT5ZALRI4FUMZPQVTAQU/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1SdJy2IcwNRwkvp76B9TAWcvo2UZxMiDdMjc3927kZ7v5ozLvZcd9HVBo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201210%2FXNK3OYPT5ZALRI4FUMZPQVTAQU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1SdJy2IcwNRwkvp76B9TAWcvo2UZxMiDdMjc3927kZ7v5ozLvZcd9HVBo&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=e96c3f21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201210%2FXNK3OYPT5ZALRI4FUMZPQVTAQU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1SdJy2IcwNRwkvp76B9TAWcvo2UZxMiDdMjc3927kZ7v5ozLvZcd9HVBo&h=e4bb45b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201210/XNK3OYPT5ZALRI4FUMZPQVTAQU/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1SdJy2IcwNRwkvp76B9TAWcvo2UZxMiDdMjc3927kZ7v5ozLvZcd9HVBo</a><br />\n<br />\n// 據英國《每日郵報》報導，雷家可在去年生下了孩子後，鼻子冒出一粒黑頭粉刺，她一如往常擠壓，但黑頭粉刺並沒有消失，反而開始腫脹。起初雷家可以為，可能是因為產後造成荷爾蒙的改變，導致皮膚出現不尋常的狀況，她也相信在等幾周後，這顆頑固的痘痘就會自行消失。但沒想到黑頭粉刺變成大粒痘痘後，數星期後，不但「如吹氣球般」持續腫脹，甚至出現劇烈疼痛，更讓她出現「象鼻」。痘痘腫到佔據整個鼻部，甚至往眼部擴散，壓迫視神經。 // <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6834ed25fc25c9385799861d796d749f98364441","tid":2323971,"uid":211578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:54:09.000Z","msg":"Wtf<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78c5cd9bd64b22b00fbc851931d81162f02d604","tid":2323971,"uid":183383,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"哩d就有圖 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df38c3b907ae0202caafdc0476624a2c198bcb2c","tid":2323971,"uid":236080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:57:38.000Z","msg":"屌，我以為打咗格打矇咗.... 原來係個鼻嚟...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0630aba92e24e6c40a3f7174cb8703bccd0168","tid":2323971,"uid":117412,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:59:44.000Z","msg":"好似Lisa<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1fa70b9f296cce28d8fcbc552c54146b5eda83","tid":2323971,"uid":374311,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"屌奶呢D就高清大圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（屌其實好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前都幾正"},{"pid":"ab43d93ea501d6c522ed71e6589b8f6930177a3a","tid":2323971,"uid":263183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:03:28.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55835865a44a6d90e2d8fa5a38741588a145b48","tid":2323971,"uid":100347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"WoWed<br />\n